          </li>
          <li class="nav-item dropdown">
            <a class="nav-link dropdown-toggle" href="/convictions/" id="convictionsDropdown" role="button" data-bs-toggle="dropdown" aria-expanded="false">Convictions</a>
            <ul class="dropdown-menu" aria-labelledby="convictionsDropdown">
              <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="/convictions/vision/">The Vision We Share</a></li>
              <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="/convictions/values/">The Values We Pursue</a></li>
              <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="/convictions/mission/">The Mission We Do</a></li>
