  <footer class="bg-dark text-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
          <h5>Journey of Faith</h5>
          <p>Christ in all. Communion for all. Connecting with all.</p>
          <p class="small">A church committed to love and nurture Christ in ALL, offer Communion for ALL, and Connect with ALL as we pursue a vision of God's transformative, barrier-breaking community.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
          <h5>Contact</h5>
          <p>
            <i class="bi bi-geo-alt"></i> 2310 Packard Rd. Ypsilanti, MI<br>
            <i class="bi bi-telephone"></i> (734) 829-8357<br>
            <i class="bi bi-envelope"></i> pastorsarahlynne@gmail.com
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
          <h5>Quick Links</h5>
          <ul class="list-unstyled">
            <li><a href="/worship/in-person/" class="text-white-50">Visit Us</a></li>
            <li><a href="/about/contact/" class="text-white-50">Contact</a></li>
            <li><a href="/give/" class="text-white-50">Give</a></li>
            <li><a href="/about/faq/" class="text-white-50">FAQ</a></li>
